title: Haiti Rivers location data from United Nation MINUSTAH
name: Haiti Rivers location data from United Nation MINUSTAH
description: The polyline data shows locations of rivers across Haiti. The data also has qualitative information on the level of water flow in each of these rivers, such as whether its perennial etc.
